snippet.title: MOTHER 1+2 CM 4 (full)
snippet.description:
I finally managed to get ahold of a full version of this fourth MOTHER 1+2 commercial, so here it is, subbed in English.

I believe there were only four M1+2 commercials in all, so this complete the set.
